                        Regd. office: Damson Technologies Private Limited , 302, Solitaire, Sunrise Park, Vastrapur Himalaya Mall Link Road,, Bodakdev, AHMEDABAD, GUJARAT - 380054
                    </p>
                    <p style="color: black;font-size: 14px;margin-bottom: 0px;">Contact Flipkart: 1800 208 9898 || www.flipkart.com/helpcentre</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <hr style="background:black;opacity: 1;height: 2px;margin-top: 0px;">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>